                      </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="banner-carousel-card grid_wrapper grid_wrapper--large">
      <div class="heading-container">
                <h3>
          Challenges facing UK rivers and chalk streams
        </h3>
              </div>
      <div class="splide">
        <div class="splide__track">
          <ul class="splide__list">
                                                                                                <li class="splide__slide" data-link-url="https://www.wwf.org.uk/what-we-do/protecting-our-rivers-lakes-and-freshwater" data-link-text="Why we&#039;re protecting our freshwater">
                <figure>
                  <div class="caption-link-bg">
                    <figcaption>
                                                                                          <h4>Protecting our fresh water</h4>
                                            <p>The big problem is ‘over-abstraction’ – taking too much water out of our rivers. Whether it’s for our homes, farms or industries, if water is extracted faster than it can be naturally replaced – and it can be millions of litres taken in a day sometimes – it doesn’t leave enough to support wildlife or the natural environment. Farming fertilisers, pesticides, herbicides and all kinds of urban sewage also seriously affect the quality of our river water and to reduce the amount of pollution that flows into them. We’re working with government and businesses to find ways to use less, and waste less, fresh water.</p>
                    </figcaption>
                                          <div class="btn-wrap">
                        <div class="btn-wrap--item">
                          <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/what-we-do/protecting-our-rivers-lakes-and-freshwater" class="btn btn--white">
                            Why we&#039;re protecting our freshwater
                          </a>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                                      </div>
                </figure>
              </li>
                                                                                                <li class="splide__slide" data-link-url="https://www.wwf.org.uk/what-we-do/climate-change-and-energy" data-link-text="Learn more about climate change">
                <figure>
                  <div class="caption-link-bg">
                    <figcaption>
                                                                                          <h4>Climate change</h4>
                                            <p>Global warming, with changing weather patterns and rainfall, affects river and aquifer levels, causing more droughts and floods. It complicates all the other problems our rivers face.</p>
                    </figcaption>
                                          <div class="btn-wrap">
                        <div class="btn-wrap--item">
                          <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/what-we-do/climate-change-and-energy" class="btn btn--white">
                            Learn more about climate change
                          </a>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                                      </div>
                </figure>
              </li>
                                                                                                <li class="splide__slide" data-link-url="" data-link-text="Find out more">
                <figure>
                  <div class="caption-link-bg">
                    <figcaption>
                                                                                          <h4>Working with business</h4>
                                            <p>We work with water companies to update inefficient water systems, and with local farmers to reduce contamination of rivers by pesticide and fertiliser run-off. It’s good for their business, as well as the environment.</p>
                    </figcaption>
                                      </div>
                </figure>
              </li>
                                                                                                <li class="splide__slide" data-link-url="" data-link-text="Find out more">
                <figure>
                  <div class="caption-link-bg">
                    <figcaption>
                                                                                          <h4>Working with government</h4>
                                            <p>Our experience in river management and planning in the UK and around the world means we’re in a great position to create solutions and help change water policies. </p>
                    </figcaption>
                                      </div>
                </figure>
              </li>
                      </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-pagination-container">
          <div class="splide-arrows-bg">
            <div class="splide__arrows splide__arrows--ltr">
              <button
                class="splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev"
                type="button"
                aria-label="Previous slide"
                aria-controls="splide01-track"
              >
